			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="to trigger Greeting &quot;you still hanging around&quot;&#xD;&#xA;1. loadlevel WLD_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;2. goto -609.13, 5.32, 382.07&#xD;&#xA;3. Talk with elevator guards and skip through the dialog.&#xD;&#xA;4. Talk with Ward Pistle.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;To trigger Greeting &quot;You don't need nothing i've got&quot;&#xD;&#xA;1. Same repro has above.&#xD;&#xA;2. Talk with Ward Pistle again.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;To trigger Nere Killed.&#xD;&#xA;1. loadlevel WLD_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;2. goto -609.13, 5.32, 382.07&#xD;&#xA;3. Talk with elevator guards and skip through the dialog.&#xD;&#xA;4. Talk with Ward Pistle.&#xD;&#xA;5. goto -646.011; 14.962; 298.10&#xD;&#xA;6. Ctrl-shift-K (kill) Nere.&#xD;&#xA;7. goto -609.13, 5.32, 382.07&#xD;&#xA;8. Talk with Ward Pistle.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;To trigger Nere Killed HasMet&#xD;&#xA;1. Same repro has Nere killed.&#xD;&#xA;2. Talk with Ward Pistle again..&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;" />
